const navigation = useNavigation();

2. You're not checking if the search term is empty before making the database query. This might be causing the query to return an empty result. Try adding the following check at the beginning of the 'handleSearch' function:

if(!searchTerm.trim()){
  setSearchResult([]);
  return;
